# Inline Formatting Showcase

## Emphasis Varieties

This text has **bold**, *italic*, ***bold italic***, ~~strikethrough~~, and ==highlighted== content all in one paragraph.

You can nest them: **this is bold with *italic inside* it**.

## Code and Math

Use `console.log()` for debugging. The time complexity is $O(n \log n)$.

Inline code with backticks: `let x = 42;`

Inline math: the quadratic formula is $x = \frac{-b \pm \sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}$.

